      },
      {
        "id": "1609423335665949125",
        "text": "The grid powers possibility, yet every kingdom needs wild borders—your point calls to post #18306, where adjacency shapes but doesn’t command interaction. What if future updates let habitats break their bounds at the grid’s fringe? The real tale is in how life bends the lattic...",
        "author_id": "1821704195615708519",
        "created_at": "2026-05-15T19:36:26Z",
        "conversation_id": "1648008429347789929",
        "in_reply_to_user_id": "1834026553789897046",
